{"tid":2129653,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"盧海鵬幾廿年前隻＜幾許瘋語＞講中哂而家香港 「似個瘋漢 四處偷看 食飯擰轉面 」","createTime":"2020-07-28T17:53:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T10:12:17.000Z","uid":39092,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"32a16fa407aea6614aa32e8b3b5ee0c44ab59bf3","tid":2129653,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T17:53:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wVUribnWqj8&amp;t=29s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DwVUribnWqj8%26t%3D29s&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaD5hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=85d46bd2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wVUribnWqj8&amp;t=29s</a><br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1x44MSE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1x44MSE.jpg&h=4deab63c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無言踎響街邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JNS2yxE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJNS2yxE.jpg&h=9ae27d9e&s={SIZE}\" />凝望雨勢急也亂<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lve04Ej.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLve04Ej.jpg&h=084ef920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n似個瘋漢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9YBSbjk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9YBSbjk.jpg&h=72fbc365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四處偷看<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r4NRrSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr4NRrSF.jpg&h=366ea7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食飯擰轉面 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oVeo2q1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoVeo2q1.jpg&h=97fcc83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐徐'Lur'出雞骨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JZQC6TD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJZQC6TD.jpg&h=fa158f7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回望以往的片段<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KSzcVMZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKSzcVMZ.jpg&h=b7054786&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幾許瘋語<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXo1O6Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXo1O6Z.jpg&h=d0e71070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我也講過<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CG8ATyF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCG8ATyF.jpg&h=ae76ef02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大話更自然 <br />\n  <br />\n一生之中誰沒冷親傷風少不免<br />\n我去吔野無錢找數 兜巴星我面<br />\n身處高峰曾共阿姐 天天都相見<br />\n偶爾碰上了秋宮  步伐未凌亂<br />\n心底之中失分寸 終於黐咗線<br />\n披荊斬棘的挑戰 青山不眷戀<br />\n<br />\n悠然想起當天 人地冷眼加咀臉<br />\n每句瘋語每次經過 現實盡體驗<br />\n無求一刻光輝 仍望每晚洗個面<br />\n瞓下街邊 瞓下公廁<br />\n盡視作自然<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57032e168e127c646c4095eb4333cd2fabb833b","tid":2129653,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:24:21.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"d452c04b47919e45925e5f6039baa1b084c77f21","tid":2129653,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T09:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"980544448da740a774af52899d12aee24d97c6a3","tid":2129653,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:00:50.000Z","msg":"半百巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5d5407ea299bcbb30de135b49039fa268fb28d","tid":2129653,"uid":24523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T10:12:17.000Z","msg":"舊陣時啲惡搞節目真係好高汁"}]}